title: Newer Homes, San Francisco
name: Newer Homes, San Francisco
description: This data set has median age of homes by census tract in the San Francisco metropolitan area. The data includes only newer homes - i.e., homes with median age of 1970 and beyond. The data was extracted from the Summary File 3 of the 2000 U.S. Census.http://www.census.gov/Press-Release/www/2002/sumfile3.html
